                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rifrazione scintillante"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">Applica</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">e può innescare le seguenti Reazioni Elementali:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Vaporizzazione</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">: DAN inflitti +2.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electrocarica</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">: DAN inflitti +1, infligge 1</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> DAN da perforazione</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">a tutti i personaggi nemici tranne al bersaglio.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Congelamento</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">: DAN inflitti +1, impedisce al bersaglio di eseguire azioni durante il turno corrente (può essere rimosso in anticipo se riceve </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">DAN fisici</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">o da </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">, nel caso subisce DAN +2).</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fioritura</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">: DAN inflitti +1, crea un nucleo di</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">che infligge DAN +2 la volta successiva che vengono inflitti danni da</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">o </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_3497420098457790883.png",
